--> Keep everything in the current format, when including multiple departments, research groups, sources etc seperate these using a comma, do NOT do this for multiple addresses, this will require a seperate entry.

--> The above rule doesn't apply to research institutes, enter either C3RI or MERI.
--> In the source column, enter your name as 'first name' 'surname'.
--> Try to fill out all fields as this ensures as much data as possibe is present which increases the potential future applications of this dataset.
